item.atum.idolOfLabor.4: This just turned into super advanced #*@&.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.7: Well I had to come up with something!
item.atum.idolOfLabor.11: Oh #*@&, I have to do a #*@& ton of fancy stuff for this. Oh well.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.12: Maybe its on one of your secret spreadsheets..
item.atum.idolOfLabor.13: Sure, if you want your world to die.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.14: There is stuff for you to do in the sheet!
item.atum.idolOfLabor.17: Need to get up early, well "early".
item.atum.idolOfLabor.21: Oh I get today off too?
item.atum.idolOfLabor.22: I'M NOT LIVING YOUR DAY THOUGH!
item.atum.idolOfLabor.26: I meant good that you weren't changing it.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.29: I thought you said you wouldn't add anymore pickhammers?
item.atum.idolOfLabor.30: Its not like we're gonna add other javelins.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.44: Oh that's doing fancy stuff, woo!
item.atum.idolOfLabor.47: He told me to see if it would make you stop making me do silly stuff!
item.atum.idolOfLabor.48: Oh god, this turned into a lot of work.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.50: I broke everything. Now I'm trying to unbreak everything.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.51: Struggling with all sorts of issues atm, so fun times!
item.atum.idolOfLabor.54: Not sure how to do that with a block.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.56: I know exactly what's wrong btw.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.57: Pretty sure it will be broken for all then.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.58: Oh good. So I didn't break that today, broke it yesterday. Good to know.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.61: Please don't push anything that is not textures atm, I don't want all my #*@& to break.
item.atum.idolOfLabor.65: RELEASE DATE TOMORROW, GO FIX ALL THE THINGS GIRAFI!
